clockwork-role-master = Prophet
clockwork-role-cultist = Agent

clockwork-master-briefing = You are the leader of the cultists, do not leave the realm where you are. Form teams, send some to peacefully recruit new cultists, others to gather resources, brass, and energy, and keep the rest in the realm. Open portals, and keep in mind that the longer the confrontation lasts, the longer the portal stays open, until it becomes permanent.
clockwork-briefing = You are a cultist, follow the orders of the Prophet. Refrain from violence during recruitment, as Ratvar points to those already weak in will. Also, avoid unnecessary casualties among unarmed crew members. With the arrival of Ratvar, he will convert them if they remain alive.

cult-shuttle-call-unavailable = Magnetic storms are preventing the FTL evacuation shuttle from being navigated. Please stand by.

portal-restricted-area = An attempt to open a portal in a restricted area has been intercepted.